00:49:16,803 --> 00:49:17,836
Do it.

532
00:49:19,839 --> 00:49:22,507
Lucas, come on.
Your body wants it.

533
00:49:24,310 --> 00:49:26,511
Why do you want me
to do it so much?

534
00:49:30,817 --> 00:49:32,684
What is this?

535
00:49:32,719 --> 00:49:35,954
Magic.

536
00:49:35,989 --> 00:49:38,390
Pure magic.

537
00:49:39,993 --> 00:49:41,526
( Yelps )

538
00:49:41,561 --> 00:49:43,528
What's going on?

539
00:49:43,563 --> 00:49:45,563
Tell me! Don't! Addison.

540
00:49:45,598 --> 00:49:47,966
He's... he's put a price
on your head.

541
00:49:48,001 --> 00:49:49,434
Who's out there?

542
00:49:49,469 --> 00:49:51,669
Metzger.

543
00:49:51,704 --> 00:49:53,238
Damn it!

544
00:49:55,842 --> 00:49:56,842
Hey!

545
00:50:03,616 --> 00:50:05,717
Excuse me. Hi.

546
00:50:05,752 --> 00:50:08,653
You, uh...
